Pasting the load test config in case it's relevant. We use k6 for the harness because the rest of infra knows it, even though I personally would have picked drill or oha for the lower overhead per RPS. Doesn't matter for this case — we're not benchmarking the harness. Here's the meaningful chunk of the script:

```javascript
import http from 'k6/http';

export const options = {
  scenarios: {
